OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fsettled, cloud spreading southwards
OL,7,Facross the whole of the region by the
OL,8,Fmorning with some fog patches over the
OL,9,Fhills. Winds becoming light and
OL,10,Fvariable. Feeling cooler overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FLargely dry and cloudy, but
OL,13,Falso some bright spells will occur,
OL,14,Fmainly in the afternoon before skies
OL,15,Fclear overnight. Winds remain light
OL,16,Fand variable.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
